text: KYOA (98.7 FM) is a radio station licensed to Kiowa, Oklahoma, United States. The station is currently owned by K95.5 Inc ==History== This station was assigned call sign KYOA on March 22, 2013. ==References== ==External links== *http://www.blakefm1025.com/ YOA Category:Country radio stations in the United States Category:Radio stations established in 2013
